name: Split System Change-Out (2–3 Ton)

name: Split System Change-Out (4–5 Ton)
description: Remove and replace existing split system. Includes standard reconnection and base installation materials. Does not include access difficulty, electrical, duct modifications, or specialty materials.

name: Package Unit Change-Out (2–3 Ton)
description: Remove and replace existing package unit. Includes standard reconnection, roof sealing, and base installation materials. Does not include crane, electrical upgrades, or specialty materials.

name: Package Unit Change-Out (4–5 Ton)
description: Remove and replace existing package unit. Includes standard reconnection, roof sealing, and base installation materials. Does not include crane, electrical upgrades, or specialty materials.

name: Tight Attic – Build in Place
description: System must be disassembled and reassembled in attic.
